Tenang.  Harap tenang.
saya pergi.

00:13:45.360 --> 00:13:46.720
Jangan...
- Ravi, Ravi.

00:13:46.880 --> 00:13:48.400
Ikutlah denganku, Nak.

00:13:54.400 --> 00:13:56.160
Ayo, nak.  - Ayah.

